node.text:
🎙 “We had an objective, a target: to renew the team. Young players, young talent with big potential.”

We sat down with Fabio Paratici to discuss this summer’s transfer window and his first months at the club. 🎥 ⤵️

node.title: Fabio Paratici on our summer transfer window!
